name: J.League Winning Eleven 10 + Europe League 06-07
summary: J.League Winning Eleven 10 + Europe League 06-07 is a sports video game developed and published by Konami for the PlayStation 2. Released exclusively in Japan on November 22, 2006, this title combines elements from the Pro Evolution Soccer 6 series with additional content specific to Japanese and European football leagues.
